# 2. Create a tip calculator program using functions and user input. Use a return statement in your function.

#Calculator program

tip_amount = input ("Please enter tip amount? ")

bill_amount = input ("Please enter total bill amount? ")

tip_amount = int(tip_amount)
bill_amount = int(bill_amount)

total_tip_amount = (tip_amount*bill_amount) 
total_tip_amount = (total_tip_amount/100)

print(total_tip_amount)